      <p>EXCISE stands out at 15 points for 6 letters — the X does heavy lifting. DUCAT uses the uncommon combination of D-U-C which many players overlook. Old currency names like GROAT and DUCAT are almost never challenged because opponents recognise them as real words even without knowing their exact meaning.</p>

